02


회귀 트리(Regression tree)¶

  • : boston data
  • url : boston house-prices dataset (regression).
In [10]:
model = tree.DecisionTreeRegressor(max_depth=3)
boston = load_boston()

#  
X_train = boston.data
y_train = boston.target

#  
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

#  
viz = dtreeviz(model,
               X_train,
               y_train,
               target_name='price',  # leaf node  target 
               feature_names=boston.feature_names,  
               title="Boston data set regression",   #  
               fontname="Arial",  #  
               title_fontsize=16,  #    
               colors = {"title":"purple"} 
              )
viz

분류 트리(Classification tree) - 다항분류¶

In [12]:
model = tree.DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=2)  


#  
iris = load_iris()
X_train = iris.data
y_train = iris.target

#  
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

#  
viz = dtreeviz(model, 
               X_train,
               y_train,
               target_name='iris type',
               fontname="Arial",
               feature_names=iris.feature_names, 
               class_names=["setosa", "versicolor", "virginica"], 
               histtype= 'barstacked')  #    : (barstacked)
viz

Breast Cancer Wisconsin Dataset

In [ ]:
model = tree.DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=2)  
cancer = load_breast_cancer()

X_train = cancer.data
y_train = cancer.target
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

viz = dtreeviz(model, 
               X_train,
               y_train,
               target_name='cancer',
               feature_names=cancer.feature_names, 
               class_names=["malignant", "benign"],
               orientation='LR')
viz

In [13]:
model = tree.DecisionTreeRegressor(max_depth=3)

#   
diabetes = load_diabetes()
X_train = diabetes.data
y_train = diabetes.target

#  
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

X = diabetes.data[np.random.randint(0, len(diabetes.data)),:]

viz = dtreeviz(model,
               X_train,
               y_train,
               target_name='progress', 
               feature_names=diabetes.feature_names,
               X=X, 
               show_node_labels = True,
               scale=.7
              )
viz
